# Project Exogenesis — environment template
# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in. Vite inlines VITE_-prefixed
# vars at build time.

# Google AI Studio API key for the AI narration layer (TD-015).
# Get a free-tier key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Optional: when unset, the narration feature is disabled gracefully.
#
# NOTE: in a browser build this key is visible to end users (a single-page
# client cannot hold a secret). The free tier caps abuse cost; a public
# production deployment should route narration through a key-holding proxy.
VITE_GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=
